  "summary": "Iranian state-linked threat cluster also tracked as Peach Sandstorm, HOLMIUM, Elfin, and Refined Kitten, active since at least 2013 and focused on intelligence collection against aviation/aerospace, defense, satellite, energy, oil-and-gas, petrochemical, education, and government targets. Observed tradecraft includes recruitment-themed spearphishing, password spraying, valid cloud accounts, Azure-hosted C2, custom backdoors such as Tickler, POWERTON, and TURNEDUP, PowerShell and VBScript execution, credential theft, SMB/RDP movement, RMM abuse, data staging/exfiltration, and destructive or wiper-adjacent capabilities.",
